QueryToExecute:
select
  arn as resource,
  case
    when create_volume_permissions @> '[{"Group": "all", "UserId": null}]' then 'alarm'
    else 'ok'
  end status,
  case
    when create_volume_permissions @> '[{"Group": "all", "UserId": null}]' then title || ' publicly restorable.'
    else title || ' not publicly restorable.'
  end reason
  
  , region, account_id
from
  aws_ebs_snapshot;
